{'text': 'Beautiful art display. I am not a person who into art but seeing the detail of the art here, I can say that the authors are very skillful and have a great sense of art.

There are many arts inside and free entry to look at the art. Quite a bit place and no crowd when I visited on weekday afternoon.

It is located at level 4 ION Orchard beside concierge counter.', 'languageCode': 'en'}

